commands:
N-No...!
I didn't mean to 
kill you ...

It seems like
this door is broken.

I can't open it 
from this side.

It's not fair. 
No one had the right to 
change you like this...
But I'm back to save you.

Okay... this time 
it'll be different.

It is not the timing
I am supposed to use this.

Oh my God...!
Who are you?

No! 
Please get out of here!

You don't have
 to be scared.
 I love you!

I don't wanna be 
loved by you!

N-No...!
I didn't mean to 
kill you ...

I think I can fix it, 
so don't worry...

I just didn't want you
 to run away.

A man just broke
into my house!

I am sorry...
I broke this door too...
So that's how you got in...

What do you 
want from me?

Nothing! 
I love you, that's all!

Just tell me 
if you could love me too...

You don't understand 
how hard it is...

It seems like
the door is locked...

What did you do 
to the door?

Why everyone 
runs away from me...?

No, it's not 
what you think...

You have to figure 
that out for yourself.

That's what I've 
been trying to do!

I know you can open 
this door on your own.

But I'll open it for you 
if you calm down.

Just stay still and 
I won't hurt you!

No... oh no, 
I didn't mean to...

What do you 
want from me!?

I want you to love me 
just like I love you.

o, okay... 
I think I could...

Liar Liar Liar Liar Liar
Liar Liar Liar Liar Liar !!!

Oh God, 
he broke the lock...

You wouldn't. 
I know you too well...

It's okay! 
You don't have to be scared.

I love you. 
Please don't cry.

Don't let him do this!! 
Stop him!!

Who the hell 
are you talking to?

Why don't you 
feel my love??

I kill you,
and I will die!

Oh God, 
he broke the lock...

It doesn't matter
who I am...

I'm here because 
I love you.

Don't look at
me like that!!
I wish I can sleep with...

I need to save her,
from... me.

I mean, 
I really don't think 
this door will open for me.

I have a reflection, 
even though 
time is stopped.

I've never been on this side 
of her window before.

I guess I can't call 
if time is stopped.

It'll get pretty dark 
if I switch it off.

There's a lingering 
smell in here...

You'll be safe 
from me now.

I can't get the clock
 to go forward.

I guess getting caught
isn't the same thing 
as atonement.

What could I have 
done differently?

She's already dead, 
you stupid bastard...

How could I be 
capable of this?

Whatever I do, 
my ugly self always 
comes out.

I finally realized.
I am worthless.

I was always 
looking at you.

but I didn't realize 
how ugly I was.

I want to atone 
for my sins...

Let's go back to 
the beginning.
I didn't mean to trip her...

Did I? 
I don't understand myself...

She was getting 
away on her own...

Maybe I didn't 
need to interfere.

The past won't 
change on its own.

I'll have to push things 
in a different direction.

I'll put a stop to this. 
I promise.
